MOVE_LEFT *= MOVE_LEFT ** LL
MOVE_LEFT *| MOVE_LEFT ** LL
MOVE_LEFT *# READING   ** DS

// 2. TRIMMING
REMOVE_LAST_ROW !* REMOVE_LAST_ROW _* RS
REMOVE_LAST_ROW _* TRIMMING ** SS

TRIMMING *# TRIMMING ** SR
TRIMMING *= TRIMMING ** SR
TRIMMING *| TRIMMING_CLEANUP ** SR

